===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|kerf}}, {{m|enm|kirf}}, {{m|enm|kyrf}}, from {{inh|en|ang|cyrf|t=an act of cutting, a cutting off; a cutting instrument}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*kurbiz|t=a cut; notch}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*gerbʰ-|t=to scratch}}.

